{"word":"πλαταγώνιον","slug":"πλαταγώνιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n83525\" key=\"platagw/nion\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πλᾰτᾰγ-ώνιον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n83525.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">broad petal of the poppy</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">anemone</tr_>, so called because lovers took omens from it, laying it on the left hand, and striking it with the right, and it was a good omen if it burst <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with a loud crack</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:57\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.57</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nic.\">Nic.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">74.43</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:9:127\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.127</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τῷ μηκῶνος π.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0526.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:7:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ J.\">J.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ AJ\">AJ</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.7.6</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (vulg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πλαταγῶνι</foreign>) ; cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τηλέφιλον</foreign>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}